Don't fall victim to #COVID19 vaccination scams!
📝 Paying to put your name on a #vaccine wait list
📞 Calls, emails, texts or ads from unknown sources
📦 Offers to sell/ship doses for payment
❌ Do not give out your private credentials or SSN
Learn more: https://t.co/048q0kJIaz https://t.co/8feVty0ZHe
